==Finnish==
===Noun===

halvattu (genitive ''halvatun'')

(expletive) hell, fuck shit.

Finnish synonyms: [[helvetti]]

===Examples===

*''Se halvatun idiootti on taas ovella.'' The fucking idiot is at the door again.
*''Missä halvatussa sä oikein asut?'' Where the hell do you live, man?

===Etymology===

Halvattu is a corrupt of [[helvetti]] and it sounds much like ''halvaantunut'', [[paralyze]]d. This can have a connection to old religious beliefs that disablilities are punishments for sin.